      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " shows, is not to be understood with בּ; בּ is that of the state or time, not of the object. Regarding איד, calamitas opprimens, obruens (from אוּד  equals  Arabic âda, to burden, to oppress), see at ",
